Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0
Constants: [5]
Expected: Bytecode object ✓
```

### 2. 산술 연산
```
Code: 1 + 2
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0
  OpConstant 1
  OpAdd
Constants: [1, 2]
```

### 3. 여러 명령어
```
Code: 1 + 2 * 3
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0   (1)
  OpConstant 1   (2)
  OpConstant 2   (3)
  OpMultiply
  OpAdd
Constants: [1, 2, 3]
```

### 4. 상수 풀 최적화
```
Code: 5 + 5
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0   (5)
  OpConstant 0   (동일 상수)
  OpAdd
Constants: [5]  ← 5가 한 번만!
```

### 5. 비교 연산
```
Code: 5 > 3
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0   (5)
  OpConstant 1   (3)
  OpGreaterThan
Constants: [5, 3]
```

### 6. 부정 연산
```
Code: !true
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0   (true)
  OpNot
Constants: [true]
```

### 7. 중첩 표현식
```
Code: (1 + 2) * (3 + 4)
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0   (1)
  OpConstant 1   (2)
  OpAdd
  OpConstant 2   (3)
  OpConstant 3   (4)
  OpAdd
  OpMultiply
Constants: [1, 2, 3, 4]
```

### 8. 복잡한 표현식
```
Code: 1 + 2 * 3 - 4 / 2
Bytecode:
  OpConstant 0   (1)
  OpConstant 1   (2)
  OpConstant 2   (3)
  OpMultiply
  OpAdd
  OpConstant 3   (4)
  OpConstant 4   (2)
  OpDivide
  OpSubtract
Constants: [1, 2, 3, 4, 2]
```

